Package com.matheus.erp.model

Class AbstractModel

java.lang.Object
com.matheus.erp.model.AbstractModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
ProductModel, StockModel
public abstract class AbstractModel extends Object
AbstractModel class serving as a foundation for specific models. Defines common methods for managing data and interacting with resources.
